quotes.text: Age is something that doesn't matter, unless you are a cheese.
quotes.author: Luis Bunuel

quotes.text: A day without sunshine is like, you know, night.
quotes.author: Steve Martin

quotes.text: Before you criticize someone, walk a mile in their shoes. That way, you'll be a mile from them, and you'll have their shoes.
quotes.author: Jack Handey

quotes.text: I told my doctor I broke my arm in two places. He told me to keep out of those places.
quotes.author: Rodney Dangerfield

quotes.text: It's just a job. Grass grows, birds fly, waves pound the sand. I beat people up.
quotes.author: Muhammad Ali
